<HEADLINE> Danish Detain 37 for Child Porn  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   COPENHAGEN, Denmark (AP) -- Police detained 37 men in pre-dawn
raids Thursday across Denmark, seizing child pornography material
that was distributed by e-mail.
</P>
<P>
   No charges were filed, investigators said. Those arrested would
first be fined for distributing the material. Charges could be
considered if it were determined that any were producing or
commercially distributing the photos.
</P>
<P>
   In Denmark, possession of pornography involving those under age
15 is punishable only by fines. The maximum sentence for producing
or commercial distributing of such photos is two years in jail.
</P>
<P>
   Ole Hoeyer Pedersen, a police spokesman, said the men likely
didn't know each other, but had exchanged e-mail addresses through
Internet chat rooms and later sent photos to each other
electronically.
</P>
</TEXT>
